                      asperiores, nihil saepe facilis voluptate adipisci 
                      possimus distinctio reiciendis officiis consequatur  optio ut repellendus!</p>


                      <div class="btn-group">
                          <a  href="/contact" class="contact-btn">
                             Contact 
                          </a>

                          <div class="download-btn">
                             download CV <img src="images/downloads.png">
                          </div>
                      </div>

                     <!-- Social -->
                    <div class="intro__socials">

                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/darren-christian-t-8b59b9224">
                                 <i  class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://instagram.com/selftaught_tj?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=">
